{"tid":1476711,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"大家一定要清楚知道點解要清算警隊，不能放過！","createTime":"2019-08-16T01:59:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T18:11:34.000Z","uid":43785,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ef81b9ba90a97cb054f728b4c6160e9ec196991e","tid":1476711,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:59:02.000Z","msg":"大家一定要清楚知道點解要清算警隊。警暴（濫捕、濫告、不依法規）係暴政一部分，唔全面改革警隊、監警制度，只會令目前同將來爭取雙普選更加舉步維艱。<br />\n<br />\n所以，絕對唔需要否認自己係針對警隊或者仇警，針對警隊就係對準政權。唔通你淨係針對林鄭、唔針對政制，就會有雙普選？"},{"pid":"e3bc0c30b94872e45ca1f378fce6e8e25aa5fbb7","tid":1476711,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:59:38.000Z","msg":"支持仇警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一定要清算"},{"pid":"aafc58281372a54cabcfddc7a291a570427eb7a7","tid":1476711,"uid":79046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:02:45.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行過路過入嚟望下，千載難逢嘅大好機會！！十八區we connect，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">823人鏈823人鏈823人鏈</span></span></strong>，百萬人齊築香江路！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［和理非升級］一生人一次嘅機會嚟喇！！！！想唔想上Buzzfeed 9GAG？！？！？！？！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475842\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475842</a>"},{"pid":"af0b3b7d48329e15362add1777b3bec9df19d8dd","tid":1476711,"uid":280572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e3bc0c30b94872e45ca1f378fce6e8e25aa5fbb7","tid":1476711,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:59:38.000Z","msg":"支持仇警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一定要清算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:03:19.000Z","msg":"Morning 9sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77fef0435d264bdc0a405dac00977527ef244658","tid":1476711,"uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:03:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FkW8NPX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFkW8NPX.jpg&h=ab57eaae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外想提下大家<br />\n各位手足切記點解要black bloc。<br />\n<br />\n之前沙田有人就係着粉紅色衫，好快就俾人認到，個個黑色先唔明顯。"},{"pid":"c95276b32105e1fe30f30c759434e3cdb3377ad8","tid":1476711,"uid":245371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:04:51.000Z","msg":"國際法庭啦"},{"pid":"4147ce17bc3bb69722dc67287da95aba39a5c826","tid":1476711,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:05:16.000Z","msg":"唔好咁天真，真係以為唔衝，乖乖仔行完就唔會放催淚彈。啱啱鬼節深水埗燒街衣就係證明，就算冇衝擊，警方都照放催淚彈，佢唔會理你著咩色衫，老人家小朋友定係小動物。<br />\n<br />\n當然，圖中呢類智障係應該食催淚彈，等佢面對下現實。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d17cu4F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd17cu4F.jpg&h=3fe8bb9a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d348bed08ea1eeddcfc84d7e1705e2c24b30f76","tid":1476711,"uid":153151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:12:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tEinSkq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtEinSkq.png&h=20f4fabb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efa952ae6e028214d03d5907cb4e900867298af7","tid":1476711,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:27:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6854e141e26571b9dfc19d973acb75baf303546d","tid":1476711,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:29:45.000Z","msg":"一定要全面改革"},{"pid":"37366d0151603193c4d747a065cdf9db091bcdab","tid":1476711,"uid":118176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:31:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0b72892e2ae20816efa05a62af68ef0e4559539","tid":1476711,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:11: